text: Dunière-sur-Eyrieux is a commune Ardèche in southern France. The commune's name was changed from Dunières-sur-Eyrieux to Dunière-sur-Eyrieux (without "s") on 1st of January 2001. ==Related pages== *Communes of the Ardèche department == References == Category:Communes in Ardèche
title: Dunière-sur-Eyrieux
